…Blame weak economic recovery, insecurity, capital flight
…Urge govt. to prioritise critical sectors, incentivize listed firms Worried by over N2 trillion losses recorded by stock market investors in the last three years, experts have urged the government to tackle insecurity issues and other macroeconomic concerns impeding efforts to attract the needed investment into Nigeria.
 
